snippet: Four former Vanderbilt football players were indicted on five counts each of aggravated rape of an unconscious 21-year-old female student at a dormitory in June.
abstract: Former Vanderbilt football players Cory Batey, Brandon Banks, Jaborian McKenzie and Brandon Vandenburg are indicted on five counts each of aggravated rape of an unconscious 21-year-old female student at a dormitory.
lead_paragraph: Four former Vanderbilt football players were indicted on five counts each of aggravated rape of an unconscious 21-year-old female student at a dormitory in June.
